{"tid":1656701,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得自己係Loser 既入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-10-15T17:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T14:10:19.000Z","uid":156696,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"08281e2979d690e272bd77ad81bbf64222acaa2f","tid":1656701,"uid":156696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:20:59.000Z","msg":"歡迎圍爐取暖！<br />\n以下係發洩文 覺得好灰既可以走先！麻煩晒<br />\n<br />\n求大家屌醒我！<br />\nDse 得15 分 <br />\n去左hkcc 讀psy<br />\n一開始已經好差 得3.3<br />\n之後每況愈下 <br />\n最後得返3.08<br />\n得ou 收我<br />\n但係ou 真係咩都冇咁 硬件又無 想搵exchange intern 都得好少<br />\n但我憑咩話ou 呀 我自己廢 日日混混噩噩 hea下又一日<br />\n明明無上莊 又無咩野做<br />\n但係成績都係咁差<br />\n到而家 已經再無心情去讀落去 唔知點算 好辛苦 差唔多日日都喊 甚至想quit 左佢 每一日只係生存<br />\n究竟係咪我唔適合讀書？<br />\nPs 呢段時間都有發下夢咁 個社會咁樣加埋自己咁廢 <br />\n我睇唔見自己將來"},{"pid":"8e164618efe6854c515b0efa90a1f68b224f1e7e","tid":1656701,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:21:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHH8FUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHH8FUF.jpg&h=3fd66e79&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9c873ab5ed9d1b77dc256bb81ec127d7b6580569","tid":1656701,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:21:32.000Z","msg":"幫推 p牌仔推唔喐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【簡易文宣】本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656652</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c83114b3243d984fbb1b439b45c63b3722badb65","tid":1656701,"uid":26952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wdLutu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwdLutu8.jpg&h=bdf4f2e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HdRYmP8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHdRYmP8.jpg&h=3ac44c9b&s={SIZE}\" /><